						"copy": "Tuesdays at 11:30 AM PT / 2:30 PM ET\n\nWhat to expect:\n\n- A discussion on mitigating attacks\n- An opportunity to learn from and network with your peers.\n\n---\n\n__Decoding AI Standards: The Frameworks Generating Buzz Right Now__\n\nDate: May 19, 2026\n\nLet Cloudflare help you decode the latest global standards for AI deployments. Future-proof your innovation by mastering today's hottest AI frameworks, from the ethical essentials of responsible AI, to new AI cybersecurity requirements. Join us to discover how to build intelligent systems that are as secure and trustworthy as they are groundbreaking!\n\n__Managing Security Risks__\n\nDate: June 9th, 2026\n\nThis session outlines the risk team's core framework for managing security risks, detailing the  processes of identification, assessment, and executive reporting. We will explore how these foundational workflows are being advanced through purposeful AI and automation use.\n\n---\n\n*Subjected to all applicable federal and state and local laws and regulations and is void where prohibited by law.",
